description:
This beat was produced only using Modular Synthesizer as sound source and sequencer. Recorded on Ableton and interactive 3D animation created in Blender.
*30,"$" is a on going series of animations made for some short beats produced with modular synthesizers, octatrack and ableton live. 


I am João Milet Meirelles, you can check my music work at www.joaomeirelles.art.br
